# .proxmoxignore — fields the sync tool will never write, for any VM.
#
# Format: vm_name_glob|field_glob   (fnmatch, last match wins)
#         prefix ! to re-include a previously ignored pattern
#
# Examples:
#   *|description          ignore description on every VM
#   *|tags                 ignore tags on every VM (manage via PVE UI)
#   !important-vm|tags     ...but DO sync tags for this specific VM
*|description